title: Internet Radio Fan v 1.04
description:
Internet Radio Fan v 1.04


The program Internet RadioFan allows you to listen to radio and watch TV broadcasts on the internet. 
All radio and TV stations are grouped by country. The description of each channel contains:

1) The name of the city from which the broadcast originates.
2) The style or genre of the given station.

The channel list is constantly updated and is always accessible for manual or auto-updating. A special button can be set for quick connection to a given channel.

The program can be minimized to tray and allows you to listen to the radio while working on your computer.

Attention! To use Internet RadioFan the following components are needed:

1) Microsoft Net Framework 2.0 or higher. 
2) Windows Media Player 9.0 or higher.

Homepage.....http://www.pingotron.com/irf.htm
